com.davesartory.launchpad

Enum LpColor

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<LpColor>
      • com.davesartory.launchpad.LpColor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<LpColor>

    public enum LpColor
extends java.lang.Enum<LpColor>
    Specific colors for Launchpad color/Java color relationships. We are storing int values that represent midi velocities from 0-127 and java.awt.color values that match as closely as possible for on-screen replication
